### ============================================================
### COURIERS — Availability Toggle, List Available in City
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@courierToken = PASTE_COURIER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@customerToken = PASTE_CUSTOMER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# TOGGLE COURIER AVAILABILITY (couriers only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Toggle Availability — approved courier toggles on/off
PUT {{baseUrl}}/couriers/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Toggle Availability — customer tries to toggle (403 Couriers only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/couriers/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Toggle Availability — no token (401 Unauthorized)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/couriers/availability

###

### [FAIL — Security] Toggle Availability — forged JWT claiming courier role (401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/couriers/availability
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI5OTk5OTkiLCJyb2xlIjoiQ291cmllciIsImV4cCI6OTk5OTk5OTk5OX0.FAKESIG


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# LIST AVAILABLE COURIERS IN CITY (public endpoint)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Available Couriers — city 1 with default pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/couriers/available/1

###

### [SUCCESS] Get Available Couriers — city 2 with limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/couriers/available/2?skip=0&limit=10

###

### [FAIL — Not Found / Empty] Get Available Couriers — city with no couriers (returns empty list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/couriers/available/99999

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Get Available Couriers — limit exceeds max (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/couriers/available/1?limit=9999

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Get Available Couriers — negative skip (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/couriers/available/1?skip=-5
